<br>
the old system required us, realistically, to start new members out at -15......merely because we COULD NOT allow the total points be more then the loot we have gotten......if we did, the system would crash.......<br>
better to fix it before it breaks ;)<br>
<br>
the point wipe system would put everyone, actually, just at 0......<br>
however you wont gain points until youre on the full members list, which will require 3 raids......which is back to the original intent of what our rules said to begin with ;)<br>
<br>
we are quite lenient of course with putting people on the members list before 3 raids.....all it takes really is to show your participation and commitment to the group to become a 'full member' (you already are lild).....<br>
<br>
so anyway, putting in this new system would wipe everyones points to zero.....must be a member (read: not still an 'initiate') prior to a raid to recieve raid points however.....and any loot thus far recieved we can sortof 'sum out' and bank it......if thats ok with everyone ;) <p><HR>
